data.description: This split foyer, on approximately 1 acre, is nestled in near the base of the mountain offering convenient access, numerous upgrades, community amenities and room to grow. The main level offers 3 beds and 2 full baths, brand new carpet, and a vaulted living space. A large kitchen boasts bar top counters, great for entertaining and maximizing the space, without sacrificing the dining area. Cozy up in front of the fireplace or enjoy ALL the natural light from the large front windows. Exit the dining area to your oversized back deck where you can enjoy tons of wildlife including deer, turkeys and bear! Oh my! And that's just the main level. Below you will find a 2 car garage with extra space for storage, & plenty of room to grow, with a bath already plumbed. A great place for your game room until you're ready to finish it out. Put this one on your "Must See" list!
